Rd8 Rxb6 26. Rxe8 $18 {White has a winning advantage. Later on, he managed to
convert it.} Rc6 27. Rb8 h6 28. a4 Kf7 29. a5 f5 30. Nf2 Rd6 31. Kf3 Rd2 32.
Rb6 g5 33. Ke3 Ra2 34. Nd3 Rxa5 35. Ne5+ Kf6 36. Rb7 Be7 37. Rxe7 Kxe7 38. Nc6+
Kd6 39. Nxa5 Kc7 40. fxg5 hxg5 41. h4 f4+ 42. Kf3 {1-0 White wins.} *

