As it often happens in the Hedgehog endgames, winning space on the kingside is
a very decent strategy. In order to complete the development, White should play
} 18. f3 {Now, however, the f3-pawn is hook. Morozevich immediately followed
with} g4 19. Be2 Rhg8 $17 {Black's kingside play is already getting very
dangerous. His position should be preferred. Later on, Morozevich managed to
win this game.} 20. f4 Nc6 21. Rhg1 f5 22. b4 h5 23. Bd3 Rb8 24. Nc3 Nf6 25.
