28. a4 Be4 29. Bd3 Bd5 30. Re1 Nf6 31. Bb5 Qxc2+ 32. Kxc2 Be6 33. Bh2 f3 34.
Bg3 Bf5+ $6 35. Kc3 Ne4+ $2 36. Kd4 $3 $18) 16. Ndb5 {A concrete idea to stuck
