}) (16. Kb1 a6 {is likely to transpose to one of the previous two}) 16... Qb8
17. f3 Rc8 ({Black could take advantage of the move order by means of} 17... a6
18. Nd4 b5 $5 19. cxb5 $140 axb5 20. Bxb5 Rc8 {with decent chances on the
