1. Nf3 Nf6 2. c4 b6 3. Nc3 c5 $6 {An imprecise move order, as Kasparov will
demonstrate.} 4. e4 d6 ({After} 4... Bb7 $6 5. e5 Ne4 {, White has several
ways to gain an advantage:} 6. Ne2 $1 (6. Nb1 $5 f6 7. d3 Ng5 8. Nxg5 fxg5 9.
Bxg5 Nc6 10. Nc3 Nxe5 11. d4 $16) (6. Bd3 Nxc3 7. dxc3 e6 8. Bf4 $16) 6... f6
7. d3 Ng5 8. Nxg5 fxg5 9. Bxg5 Nc6 10. d4 cxd4 11. Nxd4 Nxe5 12. Qe2 Nf7 13.
Bh4 Rc8 14. O-O-O $16 {Probably the best line, with a huge attack on its way.})
5. d4 cxd4 6. Nxd4 Bb7 7. Qe2 $1 {The best square for the queen, protecting e4,
keeping an eye on c4 and the g4-square and enabling possible long castling as
well as tactical motifs on the e-file.} Nbd7 (7... Nc6 8. Nxc6 Bxc6 9. Bg5 e6
10. O-O-O $16 {, for example} Qc7 11. Kb1 Be7 12. h4 O-O 13. f3) (7... e6 8. g4
$1 (8. g3 $14) 8... Nc6 (8... Be7 9. g5 Nfd7 10. h4 Nc6 11. Be3 $40) 9. Nxc6
Bxc6 10. Bg2 Be7 11. Be3 (11. Bf4 $5 Nd7 (11... Qc7 12. g5 Nd7 13. Nb5 $16) 12.
Bg3 O-O 13. O-O $14) 11... O-O 12. g5 Nd7 13. h4 $16) (7... g6 8. f3 Bg7 9. Be3
Nc6 10. Nxc6 Bxc6 11. Qd2 O-O 12. Be2 $16) 8. g3 (8. g4 $5) 8... Rc8 9. Bg2 a6
$2 10. O-O Qc7 ({After} 10... e6 {, White has several ways to gain a large
advantage.} 11. Nxe6 $3 (11. f4 $5 Qc7 (11... Be7 $2 12. e5 Bxg2 13. Kxg2 dxe5
14. fxe5 Ng8 15. Bf4 $18) 12. b3 Be7 13. Bb2 O-O 14. g4 $16) (11. Nd5 $1 exd5
12. exd5+ Qe7 (12... Be7 13. Nf5 Kf8 14. Re1 Ng8 15. Bf4 $40) 13. Be3 $3 g6 (
13... Kd8 14. Nc6+ Bxc6 15. dxc6 Nc5 16. b4 Ne6 17. Bxb6+ Nc7 18. Qd2 $18) 14.
Nc6 Bxc6 15. dxc6 Ne5 16. Rfe1 $16) 11... fxe6 12. e5 Bxg2 13. exf6 Qxf6 14.
Kxg2 Be7 15. Re1 $16) 11. b3 e6 ({No better is} 11... g6 12. Nd5 Nxd5 (12...
Bxd5 13. exd5 Bg7 14. Bb2 $16) 13. exd5 Bg7 14. Bb2 $16) 12. Nd5 $3 Qb8 (12...
exd5 13. exd5+ Be7 14. Nf5 Nf8 15. Nxg7+ Kd8 16. Nf5 $18) 13. Rd1 g6 (13...
exd5 14. exd5+ Kd8 15. Nc6+ $18 Bxc6 16. dxc6 Nc5 17. b4 Ne6 18. Bb2 $18 ({Or} 
18. c5 $18)) 14. Bg5 $5 (14. Ba3 $18) 14... Bg7 15. Bxf6 Nxf6 (15... Bxf6 16.
Nxf6+ Nxf6 17. e5 $1 Bxg2 18. exf6 Bh3 19. Qe4 Qa8 20. Qxa8 Rxa8 21. Nc6 $3 $18
Kd7 (21... Rc8 22. Rxd6) 22. Ne5+) 16. Nxb6 Rd8 17. e5 $1 Bxg2 18. exf6 Bxf6
19. Nxe6 fxe6 20. Qxe6+ Be7 21. c5 Bb7 22. Re1 Qc7 23. c6 Bxc6 24. Rac1 Rd7 25.
Nxd7 Qxd7 26. Qc4 Bb7 27. Qc7 Rf8 28. Qb8+ Kf7 29. Rc7 1-0

