16... Bf8 {[%cal Re8e3] This is good prophylactic move which opens the e-file
and protect the g7-square.} 17. f4 $4 {weakens the g1-a7 diagonal} (17. Re1 $5)
17... e5 $1 {very typical resource which you should remember} 18. Nf5 d5 $3 {
the point of the combination. Bc5 is a deadly threat.} 19. fxe5 Bc5 20. Nd4
