17... h5 $1 {Another typical idea in all Hedgehog structure} 18. f4 Ng6 19. Nf3
d5 $1 {Just in time. The start of a very nice combination} 20. cxd5 h4 $1 21.
Nxh4 Nxh4 22. gxh4 Qxf4 {The beauty of the Hedgehog is that the character of
the position can be changed with just one move.} 23. dxe6 fxe6 24. e5 $2 {
this is losing a spot, but the position is already very tough.} Bc5+ 25. Kh1
Nh5 $3 {the last touch} 26. Qxh5 Qg3 $1 {and now the mate is inevitable.} 27.
Nd5 Rxd5 28. Rf1 Qxg2+ 29. Kxg2 Rd2+ 0-1

