Nxd4 18. Qxd4 Rde8 19. f5 Bd8 20. Qh4 Re5 21. Qh6 Qc7 $4 (21... Ng4 $1 {
is the only move for Black} 22. Qf4 Nf6 $11) 22. Rg3 $1 Bc8 23. Bxe5 dxe5 24.
fxg6 (24. d6 $1 {is better, but the move in the game also wins.}) 24... fxg6
